ते<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nधर धर धिरिनिश्वराय चल चल मम विमल मुक्तेले<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nएहि एहि शिन शिन आरषं प्रचलि विष विश प्राशय।<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nहुरु हुरु मार हुलु हुलु ह्रिह्<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nसर सर शिरि शिरि सुरुसुरु बोधिय बोधिय बोधय बोधय मैत्रिया।<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nनारकिन्दि धर्षिनिन भयमान स्वाहा सिद्धाय स्वाहा।<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nमहासिद्धाय स्वाहा सिद्धायोगेश्वराय स्वाहा। नरकिन्दि स्वाहा।<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nमारणर स्वाहा।<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nसिरा संह मुखाय स्वाहा सर्व महा आसिद्धाय स्वाहा<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nचक्र आसिद्धाय स्वाहा।<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nपद्म हस्त्राय स्वाहा।<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nनरकिन्दि वगलय स्वाहा मवरि शन्खराय स्वाहा।<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nनमः रत्नत्रयाय नमो आर्यावलोकितेश्वराय स्वाहा।<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nॐ सिध्यन्तु मन्त्र पदाय स्वाहा।<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bcc7f5b45242f3aeaa416ae7b0ae10cb1b2861","tid":1296820,"uid":8301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:32:48.000Z","msg":"Մահացած սեւ ոստիկանություն"},{"pid":"5a629d6d3bda66044d625ab0871a5fbfa0cb5c1e","tid":1296820,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:32:53.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主不如搵定公民袋啲人<br />\n真係驚你出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f924e377fd2d1d2296d3e396ba6cde48c26d829b","tid":1296820,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a629d6d3bda66044d625ab0871a5fbfa0cb5c1e","tid":1296820,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:32:53.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主不如搵定公民袋啲人<br />\n真係驚你出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"屌！唔撚記得加密！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce4437cdf6678776a50f1a1d3f4b6979f72299c","tid":1296820,"uid":218082,"l